snippet.title: Wii U - New Super Mario Bros. U E3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Announcing the new official channel for New Super Mario Bros. U gameplay videos at http://www.youtube.com/user/NewMarioUEN - there you can watch New Super Mario Bros. U tips, tricks, and super-play run-through videos!
